	* m4/printf-posix.m4, m4/progtest.m4, m4/signed.m4: Remove.
	* m4/size_max.m4, m4/stdint_h.m4, m4/uintmax_t.m4: Remove.
	* m4/ulonglong.m4, m4/visibility.m4, m4/wchar_t.m4: Remove.
	* m4/wint_t.m4, m4/xsize.m4: Remove.

