	+ commit df499c6ee5edf0a560138640141a3abef360b4f5
	* tests/gpgscm/scheme-private.h (struct scheme): Remove field 'op'.
	* tests/gpgscm/scheme.c (opexe_0): Inline into 'Eval_Cycle'.
