	gpgscm: Merge 'opexe_4'.
	+ commit 5898ead4a99d3bc9e23859daf2cca9632d92f1f7
	* tests/gpgscm/scheme.c (opexe_4): Merge into 'opexe_0'.
	* tests/gpgscm/opdefines.h: Adapt.

